detail_desc: Joggers in sturdy sweatshirt fabric with an elasticated drawstring waist, taped details and side pockets. Tapered legs with shaping seams at the knees for extra mobility, and wide ribbing at the hems. The polyester content of the joggers is recycled.
Short-sleeved shirt in a patterned cotton weave with a resort collar, French front and straight-cut hem.
Hat in soft pattern-knit cotton with a sewn-on bow and ribbed hem.
Sleeveless playsuit in jersey with a V-neck, buttons at the top, narrow, adjustable shoulder straps and a seam with concealed elastication at the waist. Unlined.
Sleeveless top in soft, printed jersey with a tie detail at the front of the hem.
Short, fitted T-shirt in cotton jersey with a round, rib-trimmed neckline.
Long-sleeved top in sturdy jersey with a print motif on the front, round neckline, ribbing at the cuffs and short slits in the sides.
T-shirts in soft cotton jersey with a press-stud on one shoulder (except in sizes 1½-4Y).

Short blouse in a crêpe weave with a cut-out section at the front, an opening with a button at the back of the neck and long sleeves.Draped tie detail at the hem and elastication at the back of the hem.
Cropped, fitted top in cotton jersey with narrow shoulder straps.

CONSCIOUS EXCLUSIVE. Straight-cut blouse in a soft, airy, patterned weave made from a Tencel™ lyocell blend with asymmetric flounces at the front that continue around the back. V-neck with a raw, loosely overlocked edge, long balloon sleeves with diagonal seams and narrow ties at the cuffs. Drawstring at the hem.
Jumper in a soft knit with dropped shoulders and wide sleeves.

CONSCIOUS EXCLUSIVE. Straight-cut blouse in an airy, patterned weave made from a Tencel™ lyocell blend. Round neckline with a small frill trim and a drawstring, concealed buttons at the front and a yoke at the back. Long trumpet sleeves with narrow elastication and a wide flounce at the cuffs. Slits in the sides.
Fine-knit gloves with touchscreen-compatible material on the thumb, index and middle finger.
Sleeveless, calf-length dress in a soft, ribbed viscose blend with a slightly deeper neckline at the front.
Knee-length, sleeveless jersey dress in a viscose blend. Deep neckline with wide horizontal straps at the back, and slits in the sides.
Short shorts in light sweatshirt fabric with an elasticated drawstring waist and side pockets.
Swim shorts in woven fabric with an elasticated drawstring waist, fake fly, side pockets and short legs with slits in the sides. Soft mesh inner shorts.
Knee-length skirt in a patterned weave with a high waist, pleats at the front, elastication at the back of the waist, and side pockets.
Jumper in a soft, rib knit. Fitted style with a round neckline, long sleeves and detachable tie belt under the bust.
Top in cotton sweatshirt fabric with low dropped shoulders and wide, 3/4-length balloon sleeves. Soft brushed inside.
T-shirt in soft cotton jersey with a round neckline and a print motif.
Socks in a soft, fine-knit cotton blend with a fold-down shaft. Sizes 3-9 with anti-slip protectors.
Blouse in an airy linen and cotton weave with a V-neck, wrapover front with narrow ties at the waist, and short ballon sleeves with narrow cuffs. Unlined.

Playsuit in a soft viscose weave with narrow, adjustable shoulder straps and a cut-out section at the back with a sewn-on bow at the top. Wide, elasticated seam at the waist, side pockets and wide legs.
Wide top in a patterned cotton weave with wide shoulder tie straps and elastication with a frill trim at the top.
Long-sleeved bodysuits in soft organic cotton jersey with a wrapover front and press-studs down one side and at the crotch.
Hoodie in printed sweatshirt fabric made from a cotton blend. Jersey-lined hood, dropped shoulders, long sleeves and ribbing at the cuffs and hem. Soft brushed inside.
Metal rings in various designs.
Calf-length dress in a crinkled cotton weave with flounced trims. Deep, wrapover V-neck, both front and back, horizontal ties at the back, and ties at one side of the front. Lined.
Top in patterned chiffon with a V-neck, long sleeves with elastication at the cuffs, and a smocked seam at the waist. Lined.
Blouse in woven fabric with a collar, buttons down the front, gathers at the shoulders, long sleeves with buttoned cuffs, and a rounded hem. Slightly longer at the back.
Double-breasted jacket in a jacquard weave with notch lapels, and welt front pockets. Gently tapered waist, decorative buttons at the cuffs, and a single back vent. Lined.
Fine-knit cardigan in a merino wool blend with a ribbed stand-up collar, concealed zip down the front and ribbing at the cuffs and hem.
Wide, straight-cut top in cotton jersey with dropped shoulders, short sleeves and a double flounce in woven fabric at the front of the hem.
Long-sleeved dress in soft cotton jersey with a collar and skirt in lace. Press-studs at the back, and a gathered, elasticated seam at the waist for added width and soft draping.
Hat in braided paper straw with a grosgrain band. Width of brim 7 cm.
Long-sleeved shirt in a soft, patterned viscose weave with a collar and buttons down the front. Slightly longer with a rounded hem at the back.
Fine-knit socks in a soft cotton blend.
Imitation suede sandals with an adjustable strap around the heel and braided jute trim around the sole. Imitation leather linings and insoles and rubber soles. Platform height approx. 5 cm.

Top for a dog in soft sweatshirt fabric. Double-layered hood with a leopard-print lining, a hole for the lead at the top, a hook and loop fastening underneath and ribbing around the front legs and across the back.
Short, fine-knit cardigan in soft cotton with buttons down the front, long sleeves and ribbing around the neckline, cuffs and hem.

Padded outdoor trousers in windproof, water-repellent, breathable functional fabric with folded seams at critical points and reinforced sections at the calves and hems. Adjustable hook and loop tabs at the waist, a zip fly and press stud, diagonal front pockets with a hook and loop fastening and a flap back pocket. Snow flaps at the hems. Lined.
Wide top in lightweight sweatshirt fabric with a lined drawstring hood and kangaroo pocket. Low dropped shoulders, long sleeves, and ribbing at the cuffs and hem.
Espadrilles in imitation suede with a braided jute trim around the soles and a heel strap with concealed elastication at the back. Imitation leather insoles. Platform 3 cm.
Sleeveless dress in patterned slub cotton jersey with a small opening and button at the back of the neck, frills at the top, a seam and flared skirt. Unlined.
Straight-cut shirt in washed denim with a collar, buttons down the front, flap chest pockets with a button, buttoned cuffs and a rounded hem.
Cardigan in a soft rib knit with dropped shoulders and long sleeves with ribbed cuffs. No buttons.
Short, 5-pocket skirt in stretch denim with worn details and a visible seam front and back. Zip fly and button and a raw-edge hem.

Sleeveless jumpsuit in a crinkled weave with a sheen. Narrow cut at the top with short, narrow shoulder straps, a concealed zip at the back, seam at the waist and straight, calf-length legs. Jersey lining.
Jumper in a soft, textured-knit cotton blend with long sleeves and ribbing around the neckline, cuffs and hem.
Fitted, knee-length dress in ribbed jersey with narrow, adjustable shoulder straps, decorative gathers at the top and an open back with lacing.
Biker jacket in imitation suede with a collar, decorative buttons on the lapels and a diagonal zip at the front. Long sleeves with a zip at the cuffs, and zipped side pockets. Lined.
Thong briefs in lace with a low waist and lined gusset.
Cropped vest top in soft, fluffy yarn with a wide, round neckline.
Short-sleeved top in airy jersey with a rounded hem. Longer at the back.
Waistcoat in twill made from a viscose blend with buttons down the front and fake front pockets. Lined.
Short shorts in a patterned viscose weave with soft, wide jersey ribbing at the waist for optimum comfort.
5-pocket jeans in washed stretch denim with a regular waist, zip fly and button, and skinny legs.
Short-sleeved top in soft jersey with a print motif, round neckline and gently rounded hem.
Fine-knit cashmere jumper with long raglan sleeves in a slightly shorter style with ribbing around the neckline, cuffs and hem, and slits in the sides.
Jumper in a soft cable knit with long sleeves and ribbing around the neckline, cuffs and hem.
Jersey top with a V-neck and narrow, adjustable shoulder straps. Hole-patterned trims at the neckline and down the front and back.
Straight-style shirt in linen with a turn-down collar, French front and yoke at the back. Open chest pocket, long sleeves with adjustable buttoning at the cuffs, and a rounded hem.
5-pocket shorts in washed, stretch denim with a darker, lightning-shaped section on one side, an adjustable elasticated waist and zip fly and button.
Fully lined shaping swimsuit that holds in and shapes the tummy. Deep opening at the top and ties at the back of the neck.
Fabric cap with a motif. Adjustable plastic fastener at the back.

Padded parka with a lined, faux fur-trimmed hood and a zip with a wind flap and press-studs down the front. Handwarmer pockets, flap front pockets and a small zipped pocket on one sleeve. Inner ribbing at the cuffs. Quilted lining.
Long-sleeved jumper in a soft, textured-knit cotton blend with ribbing around the neckline, cuffs and hem.
Long T-shirt in jersey with a washed look, with a drawstring hood, short sleeves with sewn-in turn-ups, and a rounded, raw-edge hem.
5-pocket, knee-length shorts in cotton denim with a high waist, zip fly and button and wide, straight legs.
Small hair elastics in various colours, four of which are glittery. No metal clips. Circumference 8 cm.
Shopper in paper straw with two handles and a zip at the top and one inner compartment. Lined. Size 13x36x34 cm.
Sun visor in nylon with a lightly padded sweatband and elastication at the back.
Jacket in sweatshirt fabric with a hood, zip down the front, front pockets and ribbing at the cuffs and hem.
Warm-lined Chelsea boots in imitation leather with elastic gores in the sides and a loop at the front and back. Pile linings and insoles and chunky trainer soles.
Long, round-necked T-shirt in soft jersey with a curved hem.
Dungaree dress in cotton corduroy with a chest pocket, fake front pockets and adjustable straps with metal fasteners. Seam at the waist and an A-line skirt with a zip in one side. Unlined.
Tights with an elasticated waist. 20 denier.
Short, fitted dress in woven fabric with cap sleeves and a concealed zip at the back with a safety button at the top. Seam at the waist and a slightly stretchy skirt with a slit at the back. Lined.
